{"tid":1456250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家入緊機場，如果清場機場需要嘅係支援","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:56:14.000Z","uid":64831,"like":131,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"fe5c75ac0eabbcc48b8c6fdd44c14349d3981b74","tid":1456250,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:04.000Z","msg":"一直覺得前線要退<br />\n但今日全世界都吹緊散水風<br />\n我第一次覺得唔應該走，反而要留要增援<br />\n長期佔領機場，逼使政府讓步<br />\n發揮和理非力量，用人數壓倒暴政<br />\n唔好幻想以後仲有機會，下次仲會凝聚到咁多民氣咩？下次港共仲會畀機會我地入去咩？<br />\n如果放TG，清場，機場手足需要嘅係增援同包抄<br />\n唔好自亂陣腳，對象一放風就投降"},{"pid":"4878d77e993cdd5eebdd9b3cff4e7f01bc964585","tid":1456250,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"b7c124228773c88cc47811f3373545fb288274f0","tid":1456250,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"112cff23977d6c7bd03f30f27b537fb38ab87bc9","tid":1456250,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"八"},{"pid":"bf65d7508cae65a2bc45dec49acee23dca011c4b","tid":1456250,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"七"},{"pid":"344e865e3349f8fb7a607154a0795f0324aaf56a","tid":1456250,"uid":123898,"like":40,"dislike":11,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場係孤島，平時可以自己決定走定唔走，但佢一封交通就等死</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日達到目標咗架喇，唔走等比啲鬼伏你?</span><br />\n<br />\n善用不推文"},{"pid":"567808ea061508f03c2256509fadc71508e5dc10","tid":1456250,"uid":64831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:55:00.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"d3a9c349432b93e89af31d8776e155ef061bac2c","tid":1456250,"uid":34088,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fe5c75ac0eabbcc48b8c6f